CompileFlags:
  Compiler: /opt/homebrew/bin/g++-15
  Add:
    - -std=gnu++20
    - -I/opt/homebrew/opt/gcc/include/c++/15
    - -I/opt/homebrew/opt/gcc/include/c++/15/aarch64-apple-darwin25
    - -I/opt/homebrew/opt/gcc/include/c++/15/backward
    - -I/opt/homebrew/opt/gcc/lib/gcc/current/gcc/aarch64-apple-darwin25/15/include
    - -I/opt/homebrew/opt/gcc/lib/gcc/current/gcc/aarch64-apple-darwin25/15/include-fixed
    - -I/Library/Developer/CommandLineTools/SDKs/MacOSX26.sdk/usr/include
Diagnostics:
  Suppress:
    - type_unsupported
